# ロッカー取得
GET http://localhost:7071/api/getLockers

###
# ロッカー作成
POST http://localhost:7071/api/createLocker
Content-Type: "application/json"
Access-Control-Allow-Origin: "*"
Access-Control-Allow-Methods: "*"
Access-Control-Allow-Headers: "*"

{
  "lockerName":"test", 
  "left":"100" , 
  "top":"100", 
  "width":"80", 
  "height":"50"
}

